<p>Featured news is used to promote a particular item such as a blog post, news article or story at the top of the page.</p>

<ul>
    <li>Title must have no more than 80 characters.</li>
    <li>Description must have no more than 300 characters.</li>
	<li>Must have an image 360 x 240 pixels.</li>
	<li>Should have a link to a category associated with it.</li>
	<li>The heading for the featured item can be changed to suit. For example, featured news, featured story, featured post.</li>
</ul>

